sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Client / Monitor
    participant HC as GET /api/health
    participant DB as MySQL ping
    participant Om as Omise Account.retrieve
    participant Ag as Agent base URL GET

    Client->>HC: GET /api/health
    par MySQL
        HC->>DB: ping(reconnect)
        DB-->>HC: CONNECTED | ERROR
    and Omise
        HC->>Om: retrieve account
        Om-->>HC: CONNECTED + mode
    and Hardware agent
        HC->>Ag: GET AGENT_BASE_URL
        Ag-->>HC: CONNECTED | ERROR
    end
    HC-->>Client: 200 OK หรือ 207 DEGRADED + components
